narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learned in general about cosmology; gained some understanding of what terms in cosmology mean.
I developed a general picture about cosmology history and some physical understanding of cosmological processes.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course was very general, which I see as both a strength and a weakness: didn't learn anything very in-depth, but covered a variety of topics. Not much focus on what is happening in current research.
Strengths: this course provides a comprehensive survey to important topics of cosmology.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. One would get a clear general picture of cosmology from this course.
